rtant to remember your username. However, you can always find the userinfo data&#10;     under /data folder)&#10;          e.g.  name duck&#10;&#10;12. Change password&#10;     You can change your password &#10;          e.g.  pw 123&#10;&#10;13. History traverse &#10;     You can navigate your history command easily by press the UP and DOWN arrow on you &#10;      keyboard&#10;          e.g.  UP / DOWN&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;" />
